{"about_the_game":"[Desert Mercenary corps] is an open-world sandbox adventure role-playing game. Players can recruit various types of partners in the game to build their own strongest mercenary group.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/1.png?t=1731516301\" /><br><br>In the Monchi Desert, players will experience the entire construction process of the mercenary group, from recruitment, training to command operations, players need to carefully plan.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/7.png?t=1731516301\" /><br><br>In addition to building and managing mercenary groups, players can also explore a variety of scenes, fight fiercely with various monsters in mysterious caves, and reveal the secrets hidden in them. Unlocking the mysterious tomb is also an important task, requiring players to use wisdom and skills to solve puzzles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/4.png?t=1731516301\" /><br><br>As a group leader, it is also crucial to meet the needs of partners. They may have various expectations and needs. While ensuring their comfortable lives, they also need to consider how to improve their combat effectiveness.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/5.png?t=1731516301\" /><br><br>Traveling in the desert maze is an even more arduous task. The maze is intricate and full of dangers, and it is easy to get lost here. Therefore, it is necessary to find an oasis in this vast land.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/2.png?t=1731516301\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/3.png?t=1731516301\" /><br><br>In addition, it is also very important to arrange the positions of the players and choose the right equipment when setting up the formation. Only through a reasonable layout can you win a refreshing victory!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082720/extras/6.png?t=1731516301\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mercenary Corps Established","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/0224e39c8aab9420754f35db2202852efd6696cc.jpg"},{"name":"Legion of Lords","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/f42fc3cf3a3114eb506faf60e93c0d5e8019d246.jpg"},{"name":"Magic Guild","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/cd52fc9a0443da78f47428f7da8a4a360ea893c4.jpg"},{"name":"Business Methods","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/0ffd5a3d52be94b7858638437407fe4dac3a631f.jpg"},{"name":"Great Wealth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/0b6598e25fa0ac7ad08e8579b791678616741eb2.jpg"},{"name":"Warriors First","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/0185f754521f6216870693f0361d19fd63358f1a.jpg"},{"name":"Meeting the Lord","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/c2296b343d11c4771ef8c5b24824f67112af832c.jpg"},{"name":"Archery Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/61260be5484ed8d9c14b53c3e6412995647c6f9b.jpg"},{"name":"Elite Mages","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/3f6ec97c936537085d7ae217bc5c5033bdbd5b7c.jpg"},{"name":"Sufficient Food","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3082720/105587b3f7f51831fefedb80911ac0010b8c32ff.jpg"}],"total":18},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic